          </p>
        </div>
        <Link href="/tutor/dashboard" className="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-primary/60 hover:text-primary transition-colors">
           <ArrowLeft className="h-4 w-4" /> Back to stats
